                            sarafa communities — all in one seamless platform.

                        </p>
                        <div class="welcome-actions">
                            <a href="/rates/getRates" class="action-btn">
                                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                                <span>View Live Rates</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="/businesses/listUP" class="action-btn">
                                <i class="fas fa-store"></i>
